## \[Meet our team] \<-- button or heading?

```javascript
for employee in employees {
  return (
    <article classname="employee-card">
      <img src="/team/{employee.name}/avatar.webp" style="width:10rem;height:10rem;" />
      <h5>{employee.fullname}</h5>
      <p classname="employee-blurb">Lorem Ipsum</p>
    </article>
  )
}
```

might make sense to show three employees as a filler space for show more team members button? Or just have all members present here?

